      "content": "but it's not just a \"moment\" or a phase. it's permanent. there's nothing left inside to grow. it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life, pretending to be alive for everyone else's sake. if i died back then, it wouldn't even be a tragedy, right? because there's nothing really left to lose.",
