    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to believe that. everyone says things get better but i just feel like i'm performing a role. like i'm just a corpse that's still breathing. it seems so pointless to keep putting in all this effort just to maintain a lie. isn't there just a certain peace in finally letting go of a life that isn't even yours anymore?",
